    "body": "> The trick is forking your process with ELECTRON_RUN_AS_NODE=true\r\n\r\nElectron does this automatically when you use [`child_process.fork()`](https://github.com/electron/node/blob/811cfe3fcd360179d3dd436e3d80e1b045adf633/lib/child_process.js#L61), but you will need to set that env var yourself if you use `child_process.spawn()`."
